messages.messageBody:
Hi everyone! I am going to have to unsub from the list. I've enjoyed
reading everyone's posts and have learned quite a bit, however, I have also
started a new list for homeschoolers/unschoolers who deal with depression,
PPD etc. and need to give it more attention. Take care everyone and thanks
for all of the great info!

Hugs,
Dena
